land, Queen Sirikit Convention Center<br /> Monday 17 to Tuesday 18 – Tokyo, Japan, Saitama Super Arena</p><p> <strong>TBA</strong><br />中国澳门<br />台湾台北<br />香港，中国<br />Hanoi, Vietnam</p><p> In support of the upcoming release of her first solo mini-album &#39;Amortage&#39; on February 14, the BLACKPINK vocalist announced an upcoming tour of Asia to begin this March. Jisoo will be playing shows in seven cities, however venue and date information for all but her Bangkok, Tokyo and Manila shows have yet to be announced.</p><h2> BLACKPINK </h2><figure id="attachment_3837278" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837278" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837278" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview.jpg" alt="blackpink producer sinxity safer k-pop industry lgbt community interview" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837278" class="wp-caption-text"> BLACKPINK. Credit: Han Myung-gu/Getty Images</figcaption></figure>